data.description: Incredible move in ready home in the heart of Surprise Farms with 5 beds, 3 baths, loft, and office!  2 full bedrooms and one full bath downstairs for the perfect guest/mother in law suite.  Just some of the upgrades include cherry cabinets, granite counters, great room floor plan, 18 foot ceilings, tile and upgraded laminate flooring everywhere accept the bedrooms, brand new carpet in bedrooms.  All this and fresh interior paint top off the interior finishes, but the resort style backyard with lagoon pool, custom fireplace, built in BBQ, pergola, and mature landscape make this home a must see.  Show and Sell!!
